Construct a rich relational database array containing 100 distinct song objects spanning Pop, Hip-Hop, Indie Rock, Synthwave, Jazz, Devotional, and Ambient. Each item must map cleanly to this precise schema configuration:
{
  id: string ("track_001" to "track_100"),
  title: string,
  artist: string,
  album: string,
  duration: string ("MM:SS"),
  coverUrl: string (valid square abstract images from unsplash),
  genre: string,
  streamCount: number (ranging from 1,000 to 500,000,000),
  isLiked: boolean (at least 35 entries must be true),
  userCustomPlaylists: array (e.g., ["Chill Mix"] or []),
